replies.msg:
@86_longo: In the last few hours, there have been positive contacts between Milan and Donnarumma's entourage over the contract talks.<br />
Discussions with Raiola are smooth. Gazidis offers &euro;6.5M salary+bonus, while Raiola asks for &euro;7.5M. The parties work to reduce the distance.<br />
<br />
@86_longo: Gigio wants to stay with Milan for many more years. There's already a drafted contract until 2024. Raiola would like to have a release clause built in the contract linked to Champions League qualification but Milan disagrees and does not want to take risks<br />
<br />
